                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.24/47: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hibbard</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-12-10T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >December 10, 1942—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>317. Your 401, December 4. No questions were asked by the newspaper
                    correspondents at the time of the issuance of the press release and no special
                    statement was made.</p>
                <p>We are giving consideration to your suggestion with regard to a personal message
                    from President Roosevelt to President Barclay.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
